flowchart LR
    Prev([Sub-Admin]) -- escalates to --> Role([Compliance Officer])
    Role --> F1[Monitor Fair Housing Compliance]
    Role --> F2[Audit Screening Criteria]
    Role --> F3[Review Lease Legal Language]
    Role --> F4[Track Trust Accounting Rules]
    Role --> F5[Flag Policy Violations]
    Role -. audits .-> Next1([Leasing Agent])
    Role -. audits .-> Next2([Bookkeeper])
